sellerCard.oneLiner: Building seamless, responsive websites that engage and inspire
sellerCard.description:
Hello!
I’m Ammar Rizvi, a passionate Website Developer dedicated to bringing your online vision to life. With over 4 years of experience, I specialize in crafting custom websites and creating user-friendly, responsive designs that look stunning and perform seamlessly.
 
My journey began with a passion for coding and design. Over the years, I’ve honed my expertise in PHP, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, while also developing a deep understanding of WordPress core features.

I believe every website should tell a compelling story and deliver an exceptional user experience!

description.content:
Hey,

Are you looking for a WordPress expert to design, redesign, update, edit, copy clone, or revamp your WordPress website for your business?

 

So, you have come to the right place!

 

I can help you create a responsive, unique, and engaging WordPress website that is fully SEO-optimized to elevate your business to the next level.

 

What you'll get:

 

  • Hosting and Domain Setup
  • Theme Deployment
  • Landing Page Designs
  • Sliders and Banners
  • Website Sections
  • Content Deployment
  • Speed Optimization
  • Bug and Error-Free
  • Backup and Migration
  • On-Page SEO
  • SSL Certificate
  • Hack and Security Fix
  • HTML and CSS Designs
  • E-Commerce Functionality
  • Product Listing and Description
  • Payment Methods (PayPal, Stripe, G Pay, etc.)
  • Elementor, Divi Builder, and WP Bakery Customizations.


Why Choose Me?


  • Risk-Free Guarantee: 100% Money-Back Assurance if you're not completely satisfied.
  • Proven Expertise: Over 4 years of hands-on experience delivering top-notch results.
  • Unlimited Revisions: Your satisfaction is my priority revisions until it's perfect!
  • Free Ongoing Support: Enjoy 30 days of complimentary support to ensure everything runs smoothly.


Let's turn your ideas into a results-driven website!

Order Now!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I offer monthly website maintenance?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer monthly website maintenance through my Premium Package for just $60. This includes managing your site for optimal performance, fixing errors, updating themes and plugins, enhancing security, taking regular backups, and much more!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you offer a live session?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer live sessions to guide you through the process, answer your questions, and provide real-time support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do the edits include?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I offer customization of your web content across any page, including banners, headers, footers, plugin settings, CSS adjustments, blog content, and context edits. I can also add new landing pages, format existing ones, update images or text, add coupon codes, and much more.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can we start a website if I don’t have content?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can add placeholder content to your site to save you time. Once you're ready with your final content, simply reach out, and I'll update your website for you at no extra cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you offer additional revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer unlimited revisions until you're completely satisfied with the result.

These guys were stellar at managing my expectations as well as building a mildly complex site in just a few days., and they went so far above and beyond. Their extra efforts, clear communication, and meticulous attention to detail ensured my complete satisfaction before project completion. Thanks Guys

I recently worked with Ammar on Fiverr to build a website, and I couldn’t be happier with the results. He was professional, responsive, and delivered exactly what I needed within the agreed timeframe.

The website design was clean, modern, and fully responsive. Ammar also optimized it for speed and SEO, ensuring it performed well. He was very accommodating with revisions and made sure every detail was perfect.

If you’re looking for a skilled web developer, I highly recommend Ammar. Great experience and excellent value for money!
